data.description: ***Motivated Seller***Welcome to 2105 E Watauga Ave located in Johnson City, TN! This delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem has it all. With a spacious kitchen, a welcoming dining area, a handy mud/laundry room, and a fully fenced backyard, you'll have all the space and features you need for comfortable living. Situated close to ETSU, the Johnson City Country Club, and the vibrant downtown scene, you'll be right in the heart of the action, with entertainment and amenities just steps away. This home also offers the flexibility of two laundry hookup locations. You can choose to use the one in the backroom closet, perfect for a stackable washer and dryer, or opt for the one in the basement if you prefer a side-by-side setup. It's a place where comfort, convenience, and location come together to create the perfect living experience. Don't let this fantastic opportunity slip through your fingers. Take the first step today in making this your new home sweet home! Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information.
